creator: Pixzelle Studio
descriptionHtml:
Store Intelligence Visor provides secure access, interaction and notifications to your data, alerts and updated dashboards to analyzie your business and make decisions anywhere, at any time.

- SI Visor allows secure access and instant interaction to your updated data, reports and dashboards for decision making at any time. Within the viewer, you will be able to search, analyze and interact with your saved and customized dashboards to provide insights to your team.

- SI Visor allows the visualization of your dashboards, alerts and notifications with fast and fluid images that accelerate decision making.

- Connect easily and quickly to your dashboards, receive notifications and alerts of your data and movements in your business.

- SI Visor allows you to be up to date and constantly updated to monitor your KPIs instantly.
descriptionShort: Visor provides secure accessand interaction to your data, and updated dashboards
